overview.en: Betdice.one is a completely trustworthy, profit-sharing and fair gaming platform based on EOS blockchain.DICE tokens are issued once Betdice goes live.Brand-new profit-sharing gaming platform.50% of Net Profit is paid out to those who have DICE staked in every hour. Gaming creates a win-win situation for both you and us.
overview.zh: Betdice.one是一个基于EOS块链的完全可信、利润共享和公平的游戏平台。DICE代币在Betdice上线后发出。Betdice.one是一个全新的利润分享游戏平台，50%的净利润将支付给那些每小时都交易DICE的持有者。游戏为你我创造双赢局面。
